<item>
            <title>[SUREFIRE-2002] TCP client throws WritePendingException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SUREFIRE-2002</link>
                <project id="12317927" key="SUREFIRE">Maven Surefire (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The main Thread confirms a session by sending raw bytes from the forked JVM back to the TCP server in the plugin. Sometimes this async operation overlaps with another operation writing events to the NIO Channel. The exception &lt;tt&gt;WritePendingException&lt;/tt&gt; is caught by the dump file:&lt;/p&gt;


